Suggestions for Improvement 
Cleaniness: Increase efforts to keep the facility and furniture clean and orderly. 
Amenities: Add additional amenities to increase customer satisfaction and provide more options. 
Location: Ensure easy access and availability of parking spots. 
Services: Place signs around the facility to make it easier for customers to locate services.
